//  [01] Initial loop + customer input design
//       → <!-- TODO: paste learning chat link -->
//  [02] Itemized pricing — Shirts / Pants / Dresses
//       → <!-- TODO: paste learning chat link -->
//  [03] Express surcharge logic + tier validation
//       → <!-- TODO: paste learning chat link -->
//  [04] File I/O — fopen / fprintf / fflush / fclose
//       → <!-- TODO: paste learning chat link -->
//  [05] Security audits v1–v3 — all edge cases resolved
//       → <!-- TODO: paste learning chat link -->
//  [06] Single-order Termux/Linux production build v1.4.0
//       → <!-- TODO: paste learning chat link -->
//  [07] Editorial review — %d, alignment, order stamp v1.4.1
//       → <!-- TODO: paste learning chat link -->
